   "source": [
    "# Binomial Coeficient\n",
    "\n",
    "For any nonnegative integers $k$ and $n$,  the binomial coefficient $\\binom{n}{k}$ , read as “$n$ choose $k$”, is the number of subsets of size $k$ for a set of size $n$."
   ]
  }
 ],
